title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - World Update X USA - San Diego - Part 2
description:
In this video we will have a look at San Diego which received a photogrammetry update as part of World Update X which was released already 2 weeks ago. This time we will fly over the city center which received a bigger update compared to the pieces outside of the city center. If you like navy vessels I have some good news for you because you will find a lot of them in the harbor close to the city.
